title: The Story of Painting from cave painting to modern times
description:
The Story of Painting from cave painting to modern times by HW Janson


Harry N. Abrams | 1977 | ISBN: 0810920689 | English | 170 pages | PDF | 32.7 MB

Not only does it explain the art and artist but is a historical reference from the first art found from the Stone Age through the lifespan of our history. It has been a great visual of how times changed as man grew more aware of art and the beauty of seeing art with depth and meaning. This is a must for art/history lessons. Not to mention the beautiful pictures that come alive when you understand them
